flowchart TB
  Board[Board / Risk Committee] --> Appetite[Cyber Risk Appetite]
  Appetite --> CTO[CTO / Technology Leadership]
  Appetite --> CISO[CISO / Security Leadership]

  CTO --> Engineering[Engineering / Platform / Operations]
  CISO --> GRC[GRC And Control Evidence]
  CISO --> SOC[SOC / Detection / Response]
  CISO --> AppSec[AppSec / Product Security]
  CTO --> IAM[IAM / PAM / Identity Platform]
  CTO --> Cloud[Cloud / Infrastructure Security]
  CTO --> Data[Data Security / Privacy]
  CTO --> Vendors[Third-Party Risk]

  Engineering --> Controls[Implemented Controls]
  GRC --> Evidence[Audit Evidence]
  SOC --> Incidents[Incident Command]
  Controls --> Metrics[Cyber KPIs / KRIs]
  Evidence --> Metrics
  Incidents --> Metrics
  Metrics --> Board
